summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 4668 for the improvement of the alley in Blocks 5 and 6, Crown Addition, being the alley between 7th Avenue West and 8th Avenue West, from West Blaine Street to West Howe Street; under Ordinance No. 54186, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
